1
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:16,160
Zhuang Qing.

2
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,640
Sister.

3
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,200
Sister.

4
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,480
Tell me,

5
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:26,480
which comes first, the accident or tomorrow?

6
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,760
Zhuang Qing.

7
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,920
Sister.

8
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,560
Sister.

9
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:32,880
Sister.

10
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:35,240
Zhuang Qing.

11
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,800
Sister.

12
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:38,680
Sister.

13
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,720
Sister.

14
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,280
You had a nightmare again.

15
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:46,520
The chief is looking for you urgently.

16
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,640
Come in.

17
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,079
I was just looking for you.

18
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,120
Don't get too excited,

19
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,580
and don't rush to thank me.

20
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,680
This...

21
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,600
It's been approved!

22
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:09,280
Chief, you are amazing.

23
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,000
Thank you.

24
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,840
Great.

25
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:19,200
The Bureau takes your accident investigation team very seriously.

26
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,040
I've also...

27
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:24,640
selected elites from various districts for you.

28
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,720
You can take a look.

29
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,260
Director Sang.

30
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,920
Actually, as for the candidates,

31
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,380
I've already chosen them.

32
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:40,000
I don't want anyone else but these few.

33
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:50,440
I gave you the elites from every district.

34
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:54,600
But the ones you picked are notorious in every district.

35
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:57,680
Take Bai Xiaolin, for example.

36
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,770
Her investigative ideas are quite unconventional.

37
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,840
For a simple brawl case,

38
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,970
she can drag out over twenty suspects.

39
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:07,240
And this Fang Deyan.

40
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,200
He's been in the Anti-Triad Unit for so long.

41
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,480
Hasn't solved many cases,

42
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:13,520
but has received a ton of complaints.

43
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,440
Always for police brutality.

44
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:19,200
And this old gentleman, Shao Hui.

45
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,760
He's a veteran in the Forensics Department,

46
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,960
yet he's still just a mid-level medical examiner.

47
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:26,000
He clocks in and out on time every day,

48
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,330
just waiting to retire.

49
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,920
I call this making the best use of personnel.

50
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,520
Didn't I learn this from you?

51
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,720
Look,

52
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,960
aren't I the best example?

53
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,280
Think it through.

54
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,360
I'll only give you three months.

55
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,720
Show me results.

56
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,760
Okay, three months.

57
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:45,820
If I don't produce results, I'll take off this uniform.

58
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:50,880
Falling, car accidents, electrocution, drowning, fires.

59
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,840
In this world,

60
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:54,520
about 8,900 people every day

61
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:56,159
die from various accidents.

62
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:58,210
Among these accidents,

63
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:00,720
besides unpredictable natural and man-made disasters,

64
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,880
there are people with ulterior motives

65
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:06,800
disguising murder and assault as accidents.

66
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,960
Cracking these tricks

67
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:11,200
and finding the truth behind the accidents

68
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:13,760
is the purpose of our department.

69
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,409
Who are you looking for?

70
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,760
So you're the one sleeping with my wife?

71
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,720
Good morning.

72
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,770
Your coffee.

73
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,280
You didn't bring me one?

74
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,360
I'll bring you one tomorrow.

75
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,120
Qiaoyue,

76
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,440
good morning, my lady.

77
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,570
You're early today.

78
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:38,040
I had high expectations this time.

79
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,520
I could even see real photos.

80
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,120
It has nothing to do with him.

81
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,010
It's such a mess.

82
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,560
Good morning, everyone.

83
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,240
What are you doing?

84
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,040
Mr. Mu,

85
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,080
why is he lying there?

86
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,800
What's going on?

87
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,040
I don't know.

88
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,960
Is that the teacher lying there?

89
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,480
Mr. Mu!

90
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:07,920
Mr. Mu,

91
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,080
what happened?

92
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:19,800
Xiaobai,

93
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,800
catch this for me.

94
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:21,320
It's going to fall.

95
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,080
Okay.

96
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,090
Captain Zhuang.

97
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,320
Captain Zhuang, something happened.

98
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:26,880
What's wrong?

99
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,600
A relatively famous painter here,

100
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,530
named Mu Weijie,

101
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,780
died this morning.

102
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:33,080
And he died right in his own studio.

103
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:35,920
The superiors said it might be an accident.

104
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,200
They want our investigation team to go take a look.

105
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,000
Where is Shao?

106
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,770
He's already on his way.

107
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,720
Sister, is this a welcome gift?

108
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,120
Our team was just formed.

109
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,400
We don't have time for this.

110
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:45,200
Let's go.

111
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:47,290
You're just in time.

112
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,560
Time is tight and the task is heavy.

113
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,680
I won't introduce you too much.

114
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,920
Cheng Mo will be a member of our team from now on.

115
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,600
You guys come with me.

116
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:55,130
Familiarize yourself with the environment.

117
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,360
I'll leave everything here to you.

118
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,360
Help me clean up.

119
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,360
Hi.

120
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,200
Hurry up.

121
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,920
So handsome.

122
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:07,680
The crime scene.

123
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,560
Don't you need to take me to the crime scene?

124
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:48,760
Girls,

125
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,440
don't be afraid.

126
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:53,160
We're just going to ask a few simple questions.

127
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,820
Who found the deceased first?

128
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,680
Around 8:00 a.m.,

129
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,080
when we came to the studio together,

130
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:01,000
Mr. Mu was already dead there.

131
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,720
Have you heard

132
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,520
if he had offended anyone?

133
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,040
That's impossible.

134
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,720
Mr. Mu was a very nice person.

135
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:12,720
I've never heard of him having conflicts with anyone.

136
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,520
Fang.

137
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,560
You're being so gentle with your questioning this time.

138
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,400
No.

139
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,010
Just routine questioning.

140
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,640
You asked so many girls.

141
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:30,100
Did you find out anything?

142
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,880
I didn't find anything suspicious.

143
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:34,960
Oh.

144
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,480
I just asked.

145
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:39,200
The deceased cared about the privacy of his creations.

146
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:42,000
So no surveillance equipment was installed here.

147
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,200
Shao, how is it?

148
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:48,330
There are no wounds on the surface of the body.

149
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:51,360
His lips, nail beds, and earlobes

150
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,690
are all bluish-purple.

151
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:55,480
It basically fits the characteristics of sudden cardiac death.

152
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,040
Sudden cardiac death?

153
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,120
A heart attack?

154
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,880
Right.

155
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,480
This is quite a commotion.

156
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,440
Tell Xiaobai

157
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,400
to ask around the neighborhood.

158
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:07,800
She already went.

159
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:10,860
She is also checking the nearby surveillance cameras.

160
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,360
Take the body back first.

161
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:20,210
What are you looking at?

162
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:22,890
Let's take the body back first.

163
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:31,320
Your teacher had heart disease.

164
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,760
Did you know that?

165
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,280
Yes, we heard about it.

166
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,760
Thanks.

167
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,220
You guys can go back first.

168
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:43,520
Oh, right.

169
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,160
Keep your phones on.

170
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:46,820
I will contact you at any time.

171
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,440
Do you have anything else to add?

172
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:52,920
Captain Zhuang,

173
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:54,120
you walk really fast.

174
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,800
When you looked at that wooden stick just now,

175
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,680
did you find any clues?

176
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:11,440
The deceased, Mu Weijie, male,

177
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,170
11 years old,

178
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:14,160
local resident of Mancheng.

179
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:17,800
He was found dead in his own painting studio at 8:00 a.m. today.

180
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:21,600
The current cause of death is determined to be sudden cardiac death.

181
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,440
And the case is classified as

182
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,570
an accidental case.

183
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,040
What we need to do

184
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,280
is to rule out homicide

185
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:29,410
and the illusion of a staged accident.

186
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:30,640
Mr. Fang,

187
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:32,360
what about the victim's social connections?

188
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:32,800
Oh.

189
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,340
Here's the situation.

190
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,480
Mu Weijie

191
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:38,800
was a top student in the art department of Mancheng University.

192
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:39,440
After graduation,

193
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,400
he opened this Doukou Studio near the school

194
00:11:41,400 --> 00:11:42,460
to teach painting.

195
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,040
He was quite well-known.

196
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,200
Near the university,

197
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:47,560
many students came to learn painting out of admiration.

198
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,240
His paintings

199
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:50,040
could also sell for a good price.

200
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:52,140
So there were no financial disputes.

201
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,440
And he had no enemies.

202
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:56,200
No property is missing from the studio.

203
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,600
As for anything else,

204
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,800
we haven't found any suspects

205
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,960
with a clear motive for murder yet.

206
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:04,200
If selling paintings can make money,

207
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:06,060
why open a studio to teach people?

208
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:08,880
He didn't open the studio to make money.

209
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:10,080
Didn't you notice

210
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:13,060
that all these students are pretty young women?

211
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:16,120
Being exposed to so many women every day while married

212
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,760
shows that he was a thrill-seeker.

213
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:20,720
How did you find out

214
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,850
that he was married?

215
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,200
The ring mark on his hand is too obvious.

216
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:28,610
It must have been taken off shortly before his death.

217
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:29,640
Not bad.

218
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,960
The deceased did have a wife,

219
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,020
named Jiang Yifei.

220
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:35,060
She has lived abroad for years

221
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:38,480
and is currently his only immediate family.

222
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:39,600
Miya,

223
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,800
notify the family to come and claim the body.

224
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:43,560
No problem.

225
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,920
Shao,

226
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:48,000
can the time of death be confirmed?

227
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:48,840
Yes, it can.

228
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,120
Judging from the lividity,

229
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,320
the time of death was

230
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,480
between 5:00 PM and 7:00 PM yesterday.

231
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,370
Xiaobai,

232
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,520
how did your interviews at the crime scene go?

233
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:01,920
The studio has no immediate neighbors.

234
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:03,800
I visited the few places nearby,

235
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,960
and found nothing unusual.

236
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:08,360
The only suspicious thing is

237
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:10,720
that the studio closes quite early.

238
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,800
However, he closes early every Thursday,

239
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:14,330
saying it's for inventory.

240
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,640
What about the surveillance cameras?

241
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:16,960
Did you check the surveillance?

242
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,800
The suburbs are undergoing urban renewal again,

243
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:21,660
so the surveillance cameras haven't been updated.

244
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,480
Sudden cardiac death.

245
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,520
No enemies.

246
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:27,210
Perfectly avoided surveillance.

247
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:32,400
What a perfect accident.

248
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,160
Shao.

249
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,280
Based on your experience,

250
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,700
could the deceased

251
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:41,200
have died from other causes?

252
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:45,840
There is indeed another possibility.

253
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,360
For example, the deceased

254
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:49,160
might have consumed toxic food,

255
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:51,320
or engaged in strenuous exercise,

256
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,120
leading to fatal heart failure.

257
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:55,680
But to rule out this possibility,

258
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:57,280
I need to perform an autopsy.

259
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:59,410
Since it's classified as an accident,

260
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:02,160
the autopsy requires the consent

261
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:04,020
and authorization of his family.

262
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,780
As for the authorization,

263
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,260
I'll figure it out.

264
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,320
Since our accident investigation team was formed,

265
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,580
this is our first case.

266
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:20,320
I hope we can work together

267
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:21,820
to solve the case soon.

268
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,120
Understood.
